text: Janet Rayner is an Australian water polo player. She competed for the Australian women's national water polo team, in the 1986 World Aquatics Championships, 1982 FINA world cup, 1983 FINA world cup, and 1987 FINA world cup. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Australian water polo players
